config BR2_PACKAGE_IMX_CAAM_KEYGEN
	bool "caam-keygen"
	depends on BR2_PACKAGE_FREESCALE_IMX_PLATFORM_IMX6UL
	help
	  The caam-keygen utility is used to operate with black keys
	  from user space. The app is strongly connected with the kernel
	  version and expects version 5.15 by default. It could be
	  buildable but not operable with other kernel versions.

	  https://github.com/nxp-imx/keyctl_caam
